text: SFL Bremerhaven is a German football club based in Bremerhaven, Bremen. It was founded in 1975 and currently plays in the Bremen-Liga, fifth tier on German football. == Current squad == == References == *Club official website Category:Association football clubs established in 1975 Category:1975 establishments in West Germany Category:Football clubs in Bremen (state) Bremerhaven, SFL
